## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible factors affecting the sense of self. The reliance on secondary sources means that some nuances might be overlooked. Additionally, the dynamic nature of self-concept means that factors can vary significantly across different cultural and individual contexts. Further empirical research is recommended to validate and expand upon these findings.

